  "caption": "Morgan Stanley just dropped a warning that should make every professional pay attention.\n\nThey predict \"Transformative AI\" will hit in H1 2026, becoming a massive deflationary force. Translation: AI will replicate human work at a fraction of the cost, and it will reshape entire industries.\n\nBefore Transformative AI:\n88% of companies use AI for basic automation. Humans do most cognitive work. Hiring is the primary scaling strategy.\n\nAfter Transformative AI:\nAI agents handle complex multi step workflows. Workforce reductions become structural, not cyclical. The cost of services drops dramatically across industries.\n\nExecutives aren't waiting. Large scale workforce changes are already underway.\n\nThis isn't a prediction about 2030. This is about the next 6 months.\n\nAre you ready?\n\n#AI #MorganStanley #TransformativeAI #FutureOfWork #Economics",
