/svg></div><div><div style=\"font-size:22px;color:#a7f3d0;font-weight:700;\">Massive deflationary pressure</div><div style=\"font-size:16px;color:rgba(167,243,208,0.45);margin-top:6px;font-weight:300;\">AI replicates work at a fraction of the cost</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px;\"><div style=\"width:64px;height:64px;background:rgba(52,211,153,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;\"><svg width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 30\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M5 15h20M15 5v20\" stroke=\"#34d399\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.7\"/></svg></div><div><div style=\"font-size:22px;color:#a7f3d0;font-weight:700;\">Structural workforce transformation</div><div style=\"font-size:16px;color:rgba(167,243,208,0.45);margin-top:6px;font-weight:300;\">Not cyclical layoffs. Permanent role shifts.</div></div></div></div><div style=\"z-index:2;margin-top:auto;text-align:center;\"><div style=\"font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);font-weight:300;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;\">Morgan Stanley says most of the world</div><div style=\"font-size:56px;font-weight:900;color:#f59e0b;margin-top:8px;letter-spacing:-1px;\">IS NOT READY</div></div></div><div style=\"background:#08090e;padding:20px 70px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;z-index:2;\"><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);font-weight:300;\">Source: Fortune / Morgan Stanley</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;\">thegeshwar</div></div></div>"
